description: The video showcases a series of animated duck-like characters with different color schemes and designs. Above the character are three floating circles in pink, orange with a white ring, and gray. The first character is orange with brown tiger stripes, white ears, and a yellow bill. It also has two small white fangs. The next character is gray with orange floral designs, black eyes with orange pupils, and a light gray bill. The final character is a bright pink with a blue bill and a blue mohawk.
